Package: bluessh
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libglib2.0-0, libsecret-1-0, xdg-utils
Maintainer: BlueSSH Project <dev@bluessh.io>
Homepage: https://bluessh.io
Description: High-performance remote access client
 BlueSSH is a cross-platform remote access client integrating SSH, SFTP,
 VNC, and RDP protocols. Features include adaptive compression for minimal
 bandwidth usage, session recording, clipboard sharing, multi-monitor
 support, and secure key-based authentication with MFA.
 .
 Supported protocols: SSH-2, SFTP v3, RFB 3.8 (VNC), RDP 10.x
 Platforms: Windows, Ubuntu/Debian, Android
